premise_source_doc_sentence: John Joseph Connolly , Jr.  (  born August 1 , 1940  )  is a former FBI agent who was convicted of racketeering , obstruction of justice and murder charges stemming from his relationship with James `` Whitey '' Bulger , Steve Flemmi , and the Winter Hill Gang .
